== 賽後 ==
[[File:Arsene_Wenger.JPG|thumb]]對於球隊取得大勝感到驚喜。]]

阿仙奴的勝利令曼聯13年來首次在慈善盾落敗<ref name="reporttwo" />，亦是阿仙奴第9次贏得慈善盾冠軍<ref>{{cite web |first=James |last=Ross |title=List of FA Charity/Community Shield Matches |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablese/engsupcuphist.html |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation (RSSSF) |date=2013-08-15 |access-date=2014-01-11 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906074450/http://rsssf.com/tablese/engsupcuphist.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿仙奴成為自1962年的[[熱刺|熱刺]]後首支贏得慈善盾的南部球會{{NoteTag|即位於英格蘭南部的[[郡|郡]]。最初只有數支業餘球隊，因為在南部的風氣與北部不同，對於職業足球仍有保留。1893/94球季，阿仙奴（當時名字為[[阿仙奴足球會歷史_(1886年至1966年)|伍利奇阿仙奴]]）職業化，並成為首支南部球隊加入[[英格蘭足球聯賽|足球聯賽]]。在翌年[[英格蘭南部足球聯賽|南部聯賽]]成立，由職業及業餘球隊組成。自1920/21球季起，南部聯賽的頂級組別加入足球聯賽體系，成為足球聯賽的第三組別<ref>{{cite book |first=Alan |last=Tomlinson |title=A Dictionary of Sports Studies |url = http://books.google.com/?id=r_Ujf9-TmBUC&pg=PA196 |page=196 |publisher=Oxford University Press |year=2010 |ISBN = 0-19-921381-X }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=1895: Drama, Disaster and Disgrace in Late Victorian Britain |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=vYhvAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT39 |page=39 |first=Nicholas |last=Freeman |publisher=Edinburgh University Press |year=2011 |ISBN=0-7486-4056-8 |access-date=2015-03-07 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402132153/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=vYhvAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT39 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}<ref name="reporttwo" />。雲加形容賽果是出乎意料的，又指出在炎熱的天氣下，取得第一個入球是致勝關鍵<ref>{{cite news |first=Philip |last=Dorward |title=Charity Shield victory gives Arsenal important psychological edge over Old Trafford rivals |newspaper=''The Scotsman'' |location=Edinburgh |date= 1998-08-10 |page=21 }}</ref><ref name="wenger">{{cite news |first=Martin |last=Lipton |title=Fans will make it hell for Beckham |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-110696499.html |newspaper=''Daily Mail'' |location=London |date=2011-10-08 |access-date=2015-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402130834/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-110696499.html |archive-date=2015-04-02 |dead-url=yes }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。他又對麾下剛戰罷[[世界杯足球賽|世界盃]]的球員的狀態感到相當滿意。雲加相信這場勝仗對於阿仙奴在[[歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐聯]]賽場增添了不少信心，因為球會方面計劃在舊溫布萊球場舉行他們歐聯主場賽事<ref name="wenger" />。柏金則認為這場勝利證明了阿仙奴有能力蟬聯聯賽冠軍：「我們將會以相同的心態面對新球季的挑戰，這是一個好開始，而衛冕冠軍之路將變得更困難。」<ref name="wenger" />

[[費格遜|費格遜]]承認曼聯是表現較差致敗，並同意雲加所指首個入球很重要的觀點<ref name="fergie" /><ref name="report" />。此外，他對堅尼養傷11個月後首度復出感到欣慰，並對下周三對洛斯的歐聯賽事充滿信心<ref name="fergie">{{cite news |title = Arsene approves of that Wembley winning habit |page=32 |newspaper=Herald Express |location=Torquay |date = 1998-08-10 }}</ref>。[[舒米高|舒米高]]則認為接下來的歐聯外圍賽比慈善盾更重要，因為慈善盾只屬季前賽<ref>{{cite news |title = Man U on new ground in early cup clash |page=25 |newspaper=Hobart Mercury |date = 1998-08-12 }}</ref>。費格遜預期阿仙奴將是聯賽最大勁敵：「你可以說今季英超錦標將由4支球隊爭奪，但我認為阿仙奴才是己隊的最大威脅。」<ref name="fergie" />

慈善盾賽事完結後三日，曼聯以2:0擊敗洛斯，並在次回合互交白卷，順利獲得歐聯分組賽資格<ref>{{Cite news |first=Mark |last=Pierson |title=Roving role is fine by Giggs |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-roving-role-is-fine-by-giggs-1171585.html |newspaper=''The Independence'' |location=London, England |date=1998-08-14 |access-date=2013-07-03 |archive-date=2019-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518114018/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-roving-role-is-fine-by-giggs-1171585.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Guy |last=Hodgson |title=United poles apart from Lodz |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-united-poles-apart-from-lodz-1174436.html |newspaper=''The Independence'' |location=London |date=1998-08-27 |access-date=2013-07-03 |archive-date=2019-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518105444/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-united-poles-apart-from-lodz-1174436.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿仙奴在聯賽與曼聯交手佔了上風，1998年9月[[高貝利球場|主場]]贏3:0<ref>{{cite news |first=Henry |last=Winter |title = Fergie shell-shocked by awesome Gunners |url = http://www.independent.ie/sport/fergie-shellshocked-by-awesome-gunners-433473.html |newspaper=''Irish Independence'' |location=Dublin, Ireland |date=1998-09-21 |access-date = 2013-01-11 }}</ref>，在翌年2月[[奧脫福球場|作客]]則戰和1:1<ref>{{cite news |first=Guy |last=Hodgson |title=United rescued by Cole |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-united-rescued-by-cole-1071629.html |newspaper=''The Independence'' |location=London |date=1999-02-18 |access-date=2013-01-11 |archive-date=2019-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412205047/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-united-rescued-by-cole-1071629.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[1998–99賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|1998/99球季英超冠軍]]爭奪戰至最後一週，曼聯最終以2:1擊敗熱刺，以一分之差力壓阿仙奴重奪冠軍<ref>{{cite news |first1=Oliver |last1=Holt |first2=Matt |last2=Dickinson |title=One down, two to go for United |newspaper=''The Times'' |location=London, England |date=1999-05-17 |page=25 }}</ref>。兩軍在本季還在足總盃準決賽兩度碰頭，在首場賽事互交白卷而需要重賽<ref>{{cite news |first=Oliver |last=Holt |title=Odds grow longer on treble chance |page=29 |newspaper=''The Times'' |location=London, England |date= 1999-04-12 }}</ref>。曼聯憑藉[[傑斯|傑斯]]於加時取得的入球奠定勝局<ref>{{cite news |title=Giggs magic sinks Gunners |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_cup/319696.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=1999-04-14 |access-date=2013-01-11 |archive-date=2003-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030409232551/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_cup/319696.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後曼聯在決賽以2:0擊敗{{fc|紐卡素}}奪得足總盃冠軍<ref>{{cite news |title=Double joy for United |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_cup/350192.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=1999-05-22 |access-date=2014-05-23 |archive-date=2008-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212221926/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/fa_cup/350192.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歐聯方面，阿仙奴只能在分組賽止步<ref>{{cite news |first=Steve |last=Tongue |title=Parlour off as Arsenal go out |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-parlour-off-as-arsenal-go-out-1187462.html |newspaper=''The Independence'' |location=London |date=1998-11-26 |access-date=2014-08-03 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305232637/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football-parlour-off-as-arsenal-go-out-1187462.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曼聯卻殺入[[1999年歐洲聯賽冠軍盃決賽|決賽]]對戰[[拜仁慕尼黑|拜仁慕尼黑]]，憑著補時階段連下兩城，以2:1反勝對手，第二度捧走歐聯獎盃<ref>{{cite news |title=Treble joy for United fans |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/353844.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=1999-05-27 |access-date=2013-07-03 |archive-date=2007-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070227131700/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/353844.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曼聯最終以「[[三冠王_(足球)|三冠王]]」完成球季<ref>{{cite news |title=United crowned kings of Europe |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/353842.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=1999-05-26 |access-date=2013-07-03 |archive-date=2008-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206134427/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sport/football/353842.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

